---
title: Ultimate Creamy Fish Pie with Peas, Leek and Baby Leaf Salad
description: Looking for a taste of everyday luxury? This Ultimate Creamy Fish Pie is our best ever version, with premium ingredients for an extra special twist on a classic recipe.

Say hello to a fresh ingredient - fish pie mix! Delicious in fish pies but also all kinds of seafood dishes, this versatile mix contains flavoursome haddock, delicate cod and flaky salmon.
